{"tid":585951,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"黃毓民：投俾梁天琦個啲係本土派既票？係黃毓民既票！","createTime":"2018-03-09T06:23:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-12T05:06:18.000Z","uid":11830,"like":10,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"7aa7d91895b4839090b490a239c2e0d99073f2a0","tid":585951,"uid":11830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T06:23:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=317&amp;v=yIPzLVqZ2bI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Ftime_continue%3D317%26v%3DyIPzLVqZ2bI&d=r0zjJVD0uMBiPm%2BTbH9UJf7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=6905c658\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=317&amp;v=yIPzLVqZ2bI</a><br />\n<br />\n5:33 嗰六萬六千票，即係投俾梁天琦嘅，好撚多報紙寫到不盡不實。嗰陣時本土派都未成形呀，屌你本土派，好撚多係黃毓民嘅票呀！<br />\n<br />\n15:07 你都唔係本土派既代言人呀梁頌恆，你都冇guts，你應該去選<br />\n<br />\n15:52 如果你青年新政仲有支持者既話，你啲支持者就唔應該投俾范國威啦。如果你本民前仲有支持者，你啲支持者就唔應該投俾佢啦。<br />\n<br />\n16:09 梁天琦後來已經變成，都同泛民有計傾啦，梁天琦後來覺得有啲諗法，覺得大家陷入咁既環境，冇辦法唔團結啦佢覺得。佢試下叫佢支持者呼籲投范國威，係我就搵個時間去法庭俾啲面色佢睇。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n完全係死廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 差啲以為新東個席係佢"},{"pid":"41c475e73f7c62eeb727f075dc820b3c9cbe023d","tid":585951,"uid":39800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T06:36:49.000Z","msg":"一早講左今次補選齊齊手寫毓民集氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3ccd7616b8cccc114d377334a6f3bd9cf93c842","tid":585951,"uid":42734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T11:33:58.000Z","msg":"笑撚死"},{"pid":"7d30bd2946a401843c9eb6cb0464e6449859ad63","tid":585951,"uid":53238,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T11:39:18.000Z","msg":"但當時你撐嘅陳云根得 22000<br />\n算啦教主<br />\n都已經輸左要收山屈喺網台<br />\n就唔好成日網上打飛機"},{"pid":"8cca4a219429915b8f1f0287b8adbaf8f97b1440","tid":585951,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T11:40:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"02931b8e4bc5d5750